- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper discusses the behavior and capabilities of robots, specifically in the context of energy foraging.
- cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) is also likely as the paper discusses cooperation and competition among swarm agents.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper discusses the emergence of new functional capabilities in symbiotic organisms.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper discusses autonomous aggregation and disaggregation of microrobots.
- cs.ET (Emerging Technologies) is a possibility as the paper discusses a new kind of collective system demonstrated by bacteria and fungi.
